7. Category Structure, Document Organization, and Final Statement
7.1 Site Configuration Document category structure
The populated Site Configuration Document contains these categories:
•	Design Configuration — Family, Scheme, Preset, Typography Usage Configuration, Current Design Selection, Design Rules
•	Identity and Brand Configuration
•	Navigation Configuration
•	Content Ordering and Display Fallback Configuration
•	Operational Configuration
